WEBVTT

00:09:58.507 --> 00:10:00.937
na kisha unapopima uzito kwa mara ya kwanza,

00:10:00.961 --> 00:10:02.625
na umepoteza paundi 20.

00:10:03.007 --> 00:10:04.789
Unajisikia hausimamishwiki.

00:10:06.697 --> 00:10:11.034
Sasa, baadhi yenu mnaweza kufikiria
hili haliwahusu.

00:10:11.058 --> 00:10:12.408
Wewe sio Mkenya.

00:10:12.432 --> 00:10:14.574
Huna nia ya kuwa mwekezaji.

00:10:14.598 --> 00:10:16.560
Lakini kufikiri na mimi japo mara moja tu.

00:10:17.314 --> 00:10:20.766
Lini mara ya mwisho
ulipotumia huduma ya serikali?

00:10:21.980 --> 00:10:24.756
Labda kupata leseni ya udereva,

00:10:24.780 --> 00:10:28.348
kufanya mahesabu ya kodi peke yako.